    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the showroom sticker shock? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it is absolutely stunning! It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage, detailed regularly, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the assembly line. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh car smell! Come see it for yourself; I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love at first sight!",
