    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirls, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather still retains its factory scent, and there is absolutely no bolster wear or sun fading on the dashboard. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having followed a rigorous dealer-only maintenance schedule with all records included. It drives tight and responsive, with smooth shifts and a quiet, refined idle. Included are all original keys, the window sticker, and a custom car cover. This is a 'no-excuses' car for the discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
